div.p:
Our objectives in Korea are: 

—To keep South Korea out of hostile hands;

—To reduce the probability of large-scale North-South
                                    hostilities;

—To maintain a stable compromise among the great powers with
                                    interests in Korea;

—To increase ROK ability to
                                    defend itself;

—To promote South Korean economic and political
                                    development;

—To encourage a greater Japanese contribution to ROK security and prosperity.
